docs {
  ## Create Recipe
  สร้างสูตรอาหารใหม่เชื่อมโยงสินค้าเป็นส่วนผสมพร้อมปริมาณและขั้นตอนการเตรียม

  Creates a new recipe linking products as ingredients with specified quantities and preparation steps for menu costing and inventory tracking.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "code": "RCP-001",
    "name": "Tom Yum Kung",
    "description": "Classic Thai spicy shrimp soup",
    "note": "Best served hot with jasmine rice",
    "is_active": true,
    "category_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
    "cuisine_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
    "difficulty": "MEDIUM",
    "base_yield": 4,
    "base_yield_unit": "portion",
    "prep_time": 15,
    "cook_time": 20,
    "total_ingredient_cost": 120.00,
    "labor_cost": 30.00,
    "overhead_cost": 10.00,
    "cost_per_portion": 40.00,
    "suggested_price": 180.00,
    "selling_price": 175.00,
    "target_food_cost_percentage": 30.0,
    "deduct_from_stock": true,
    "status": "DRAFT"
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 201,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | Request body fails validation |
  | 401 | Bearer token is missing or invalid |
  | 403 | User lacks recipe create permission |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}
